Name: The Finale that Fails to Reach
AttributesDescription:
Each time defeating a target increases ATK of all Resonators in the team by 9%, stacking up to 10 times.

This Token can be used up to 2 times in Whimpering Wastes.
BgDescription: "Mary, by the time you read this letter, everything will have already settled. Do not mourn for me. I have given my life willingly, alongside my comrades, to defend the glory of the Sentinel. We will ascend to the heavens and stand beside Them."
